name: Minangkabau Flower Garden
description:
Part 1/3 of "Nusantara Flower Garden" series.

This illustration represents one ethnic group named Minangkabau.
This ethnic group is in the province of West Sumatra, Indonesia.
Minangkabau can make the most delicious food in the world namely "Rendang"
